casebody.data:
John M. Buckingham, Respondent, v. Thomas Denny et al., Appellants.

(Argued

; decided September 11, 1871.) S. Hcmd, for appellants. jy. O. Moak, for respondent. Decided upon the ground that the only material questions were those of fact, which were disposed of below. Beckham, J.,

reads opinion for affirmance.

All concur.

Judgment affirmed.
